tiers.ability_description: At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are First Order at the start of battle, First Order allies gain Damage Immunity for 2 turns. Whenever a First Order ally is critically hit, all First Order allies gain 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter. Whenever a First Order ally attacks out of turn, all First Order allies gain 10% Offense (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter.

First Order SF TIE Pilot has +100% Potency. While allied Supreme Leader Kylo Ren is active, First Order SF TIE Pilot can't be defeated. While First Order allies have Advantage, they ignore Taunt.

Whenever the ally in the Leader slot or First Order SF TIE Pilot is damaged while they have Advantage, Stun that enemy for 1 turn, which can't be resisted. Whenever an enemy is Stunned, First Order SF TIE Pilot's abilities gain 5% bonus damage (stacking, max 200%), he and the ally in the Leader slot gain 10% Max Health until the end of the encounter, and if the ally in the Leader slot is Supreme Leader Kylo Ren, he gains 5% Ultimate Charge. Whenever a Stunned enemy is defeated, they can't be revived, the ally in the Leader slot gains a bonus turn, and the allied Leader and First Order SF TIE Pilot recover 100% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.

Whenever Imperial Trooper allies are revived, they gain 25% Turn Meter, Protection Over Time (25%) for 2 turns, and reduce their cooldowns by 1. All allies recover 50% Health and Protection, dispel all buffs on all enemies, and inflict Buff Immunity on them for 2 turns.

At the start of battle, Jawa allies gain 100% bonus Protection until the end of the encounter and all enemies are inflicted with Provoked for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever a Jawa ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Jawa allies gain Foresight for 1 turn. Whenever an enemy is inflicted with Thermal Detonators, Jawa allies gain 10% Defense and Offense (stacking, max 300%). At the start of each turn, if a Jawa ally has 50% or less Health, damage they receive is reduced by 75% (excluding percent health damage and massive damage) until the end of the turn.

Whenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, which can't be evaded, Jawa allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and that enemy is inflicted with an aditional Thermal Detonator for 1 turn, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted.
Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever Pirate allies damage all enemies with an ability, they grant Tenacity Up for 2 turns to all allies.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever First Order allies Stun an enemy, they gain Speed Up and Offense Up for 2 turns and inflict Expose for 2 turns at the end of that turn, which can't be evaded.
First Order Executioner has +5% Max Health and Max Protection per Relic Amplifier level, and damage they receive is decreased by 15%.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.
Whenever Count Dooku gains Stealth, they recover 100% Protection.

At the start of each encounter, Dengar inflicts Doubt on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded, dispelled, or resisted.

Whenever an enemy evades Dengar's attack or resists a debuff, all enemies are inflicted with a stack of Damage Over Time and Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Zam always critically hits if able. The first time Zam is defeated while there are any active allies, Zam revives with 100% Health and Stealths for 3 turns.

Whenever Zam inflicts an enemy with Thermal Detonators, she gains 10% Defense and Offense (stacking) for the rest of the encounter, and there is a 50% chance to inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns.

At the start of his turn, Boba Fett dispels all buffs on allies and grants them Defense Up, Heal Over Time, and Speed Up for 2 turns.

For each enemy with a Thermal Detonator, they lose 3% Defense and Tenacity.

Whenever an ally is critically hit, they gain Protection Up (25%, stacking) for 1 turn.

At the start of battle, if Boba Fett is in the Leader slot: All allies gain 200% Defense. Whenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, all allies recover 10% Health and Protection, gain 10% Turn Meter, and there is an 80% chance that enemy is inflicted with a Thermal Detonator for 1 turn, which can't be dispelled, prevented, or resisted.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.

Whenever Resistance Trooper uses his Basic ability on his turn, he Exposes the target enemy for 2 turns. Whenever Resistance Trooper attacks an Exposed enemy, all other allies gain 20% Turn Meter, Resistance Trooper has a 50% chance to attack again and Expose a random enemy for 1 turn.

Whenever Resistance Trooper falls below 50% for the first time, he gains Damage Immunity and Health Steal Up for 2 turns and all other allies gain Evasion Up for 2 turns.
Dark Side allies start the battle with Protection Up (20%) for 2 turns.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.
